That's the same image from the thread: http://greatmaps.codeplex.com/Thread/View.aspx?ThreadId=211166

How do I remove these gaps? I'm using "standard" way of getting WMS tiles (GMaps.cs)

var px1 = ProjectionForWMS.FromTileXYToPixel(pos);
